body_html:
I think the problem was my cpu does not support the new AVX instructions. I found a tensorflow 1.0.0 on github and installed that instead of "pip instasll tensorflow". Now, tensorflow imports fine.
So the new tensorflow packages no longer work with cpu's that don't have avx instructions? I am guessing this is what is causing these problems.

So the new tensorflow packages no longer work with cpu's that don't have avx instructions? I am guessing this is what is causing these problems.
